{"tid":2123266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★山景邨連續4年傳屎味  7樓住戶亦聞到！！！","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T04:14:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"061755ecd421944df44fd5e1e8474afb5b28317a","tid":2123266,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"屯門區區議員黃丹晴指，自去年6月起，陸續接獲街坊投訴，指山景邨近景樂樓一帶經常傳出異味，臭味甚至飄至景樂樓的7層住戶亦聞到，屯門社區網絡成員羅焯勇更表示：<span class=\"xx-large\">「一經過就好大陣屎味」。</span><br />\n<br />\n黃丹晴表示，有居民指異味問題已至少存在4年，管理處曾於今年派人到景樂樓一帶通渠，惟不久後又再傳出異味，「估計應該不是渠的問題，但不知道源頭為何。」黃丹晴補充，山景邨衛生環境欠佳，近輕鐵路軌一帶又有垃圾堆積問題，不少居民擔心邨內衛生差，會加快傳播疫情，「好多人驚之前青衣長安邨Y型渠事件重演」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/502318/%E5%B1%B1%E6%99%AF%E9%82%A8%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C4%E5%B9%B4%E5%82%B3%E7%95%B0%E5%91%B3-%E9%82%A8%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%86%82%E8%AE%8A%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%932-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F502318%2F%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2599%25AF%25E9%2582%25A8%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%2591%25B3-%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2586%2582%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25A8%25932-0&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxVuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=71cc0db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/502318/%E5%B1%B1%E6%99%AF%E9%82%A8%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C4%E5%B9%B4%E5%82%B3%E7%95%B0%E5%91%B3-%E9%82%A8%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%86%82%E8%AE%8A%E5%BA%B7%E7%BE%8E%E6%A8%932-0</a>"},{"pid":"26684c1cbc5f637574f63c67502fb962ab9aff48","tid":2123266,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmo